    </p>

    <hr>

    <h1>
      Dayly
      <a href="https://github.com/bgamwell/dayly-app" target="_blank" class="btn btn-social-icon btn-github" id="github-icon">
        <i class="fa fa-github"></i>
      </a>
    </h1>
    <p>
      Dayly is an app that gets rid of the number one excuse behind not keeping a daily log or diary: time. Dayly challenges users to record their day's activities in 60 characters or fewer. <a href="https://dayly-app.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank">Live preview [...]</a>
